-- Lufthansa Pilot Reported Fire as Cargo Plane Crashed on Landing in Riyadh
-- Inal Ersan
-- 2010-07-27T11:13:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/lufthansa-pilot-reported-fire-as-cargo-plane-crashed-on-landing-in-riyadh.html

          
          
             The pilot of a crashed Deutsche
Lufthansa AG freight aircraft reported a fire in the cargo bay
of the plane to the Saudi authorities, a Saudi civil aviation
spokesman told Al Arabiya television today.  
 The aircraft flew to the King Khaled International Airport
from Frankfurt and crashed upon landing, said the spokesman
Khaled al-Khaibari. Both the pilot and his assistant were taken
to hospital, and the aircraft was gutted.  
